Christian Mechanism Design is an idea taken to its logical conclusion.
Copyright protects expression, not ideas, and the thing that matters here is the
idea, which copyright cannot touch regardless. So nothing here is claimed.

Take it, build on it, ship it. No permission needed, no attribution required.
The point was never to own it. The point was for it to be true, and to spread.

